Call the Lockheed Martin Employee Service Center at 1-866-LMC-2363. 
Log into Benefits Services through LMPeople

 
Retirees: Retirees with questions can get information at the following:

Benefits Services Online
Contact the Lockheed Martin Employee Service Center at 1-866-LMC-2363
W-2 Information: W-2s for retirees and employees who left Lockheed Martin in the previous year will be mailed to their last known address in LMPeople.  To  update your address, or if you have any further questions, please contact the Lockheed Martin Employee Service Center at 1-866-LMC-2363.

 
Employment Verification: For employment and income verification on our employees:

Visit www.theworknumber.com
Call 1-800-367-5690


Lockheed Martin’s Employer Code is 11102. Please note that a Salary Key is required for proof of employment plus income.  Employees may get a Salary Key by visiting www.theworknumber.com/employees or calling 1-800-367-2884.

Ethics: For inquiries about the Ethics Program, compliance training or awareness training, email corporate.ethics@lmco.com.
 
 
 
