Community Relations/Donations: For information on our funding guidelines, please visit the philanthropy page or email community.relations@lmco.com.
 
Financial Questions: Questions related to the financial statements of Lockheed Martin Corporation should be directed to Investor Relations at investor.relations@lmco.com. If you would like a copy of Lockheed Martin printed financial records please see our online request form at Printed Financial Materials.
 
