Lockheed Martin Investment Management Company: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 2:20 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Lockheed Martin Investment Management Company



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lockheed Martin Investment Management Company operates as an asset management arm of Lockheed Martin Corporation. The firm provides advisory services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to pension and profit sharing plans and trusts. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, alternative investments, and derivatives markets across the globe. Lockheed Martin Investment Management was founded in 1997 and is based in Bethesda, Maryland.


6550 Rock Spring DriveSuite 400Bethesda, MD 20817-1814United StatesFounded in 1997



Phone: 301-571-7147

Fax: 301-571-7170








